doc.title: serivisi zo hanze
doc.description: Iyo ukanze umurongo, urashobora kumenyesha serivise yo hanze ko umurongo wakanze. Urashobora gukoresha iyi mikorere niba ukeneye guhindura mushakisha kugirango urebe.

service.title: Ukeneye serivisi yo hanze kugirango ushyire mubikorwa iki gikorwa, dutanga verisiyo ya beta ya serivisi
service.linkExplain: Urashobora gukuramo porogaramu ijyanye na sisitemu y'imikorere ukoresha. Ntabwo byemejwe ko ishobora gukora mubisanzwe munsi ya sisitemu zose Niba uhuye nibibazo, niba ushobora kumva ururimi rwa programme {{0}}, urashobora gukuramo code yinkomoko hanyuma ukayikora wenyine.

sendParams.title: Iyo guhuza gukanda, ikintu kizoherezwa hanze ukoresheje {{0}}, gikubiyemo ibiranga bikurikira:
